  <title xml:lang="EN">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Improving SDGs in developing countries through corporate benchmarking</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2" xml:lang="EN">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">To contribute to a society that values the success of business by what it contributes to the world by building a movement to measure and incentivise business impact towards a sustainable future that works for everyone. The immediate objective of the grant is to ensure improved social and economic conditions on people, workers, communities and the environment in developing countries through improved SDG performance by large companies by way of corporate benchmarking.</narrative>
  </description>
